snippet.textDisplay: Hey Morgan! I'm not sure what your plans are, if you do want to continue any of this or not, but I know a person that what they do is they eat vegan foods at home but when they go out to eat, they let themselves eat anything. You could do that, so you're still eating healthy but you're letting yourself have those breaks and you don't have to feel socially outcasted for not being able to eat at specific places. I doubt you'll actually see this, but I still figured it'd be good to share incase anyone else felt the same way.
